                     <interp inst="t17990508-27-off161" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17990508-27-cd162" type="crimeDate">12th of April</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17990508-27-off161 t17990508-27-cd162"></join>, seventy yards of superfine broad cloth, value 60l.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17990508-27-victim393" type="victimName">
                     William 
                     Lee
                  <interp inst="t17990508-27-victim393" type="surname" value="Lee"></interp>
